---
import Experience from "../components/experience.astro";
import Skill from "../components/skill.astro";
import Project from "../components/project.astro";
---

<main>
  <section id="info">
    <h3 class="section-title">About me</h3>
    <article id="about-container">
      <p>
        I am a front-end developer with two years of experience creating user-friendly and responsive web applications,  working with technologies like Javascript, HTML, CSS, React, Angular +2, Python, C#. iâ€™m looking to work with international companies where i can have the opportunity to contribute and focus on new challenges to keep me growing as a developer. I'm sure that i can bring value to your company with my creativity, problem-solving skills and attention to detail.
